title: Indonesia GDP From Construction
description: GDP from Construction in Indonesia increased to 279993.90 IDR Billion in the third quarter of 2022 from 267374.40 IDR Billion in the second quarter of 2022. GDP from Construction in Indonesia averaged 227320.14 IDR Billion from 2010 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 293957.40 IDR Billion in the fourth quarter of 2019 and a record low of 149919 IDR Billion in the first quarter of 2010. This page provides the latest reported value for - Indonesia Gdp From Construction - plus previous releases, historical high and low, short-term forecast and long-term prediction, economic calendar, survey consensus and news.
author: Statistics Indonesia
